## 4. AI Studio Module ✨

The Studio is the seller's **creative workspace** — one unified place to generate product images, titles, descriptions, captions, and remove backgrounds. All generation is tracked, usage-limited by subscription tier, and async via Celery.

### 4.1 `studio_generations` table

| Column | Type | Constraints | Notes |
|--------|------|------------|-------|
| `id` | UUID | PK | |
| `seller_id` | UUID | FK → seller_profiles | |
| `product_id` | UUID | FK → products, nullable | Can generate without a product |
| `generation_type` | ENUM | NOT NULL | `image`, `title`, `description`, `caption`, `background_removal` |
| `input_data` | JSONB | NOT NULL | Prompt, product context, image ref |
| `output_data` | JSONB | nullable | Generated result (text or image URL) |
| `status` | ENUM | DEFAULT 'pending' | `pending`, `processing`, `completed`, `failed` |
| `ai_model` | VARCHAR(50) | nullable | `gpt-4o-mini`, `dall-e-3`, `removebg` |
| `tokens_used` | INTEGER | nullable | For billing/tracking |
| `cost_cents` | INTEGER | nullable | Estimated cost in cents |

### 4.2 Studio API Endpoints (`/api/v1/studio`)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|--------|----------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/generate/title` | JWT (seller) | Generate product title from image + category |
| POST | `/generate/description` | JWT (seller) | Generate description from title + image + category |
| POST | `/generate/caption` | JWT (seller) | Generate social media caption with hashtags |
| POST | `/generate/image` | JWT (seller) | Generate product image from text prompt |
| POST | `/background-remove` | JWT (seller) | Remove background from uploaded image |
| POST | `/enhance` | JWT (seller) | Full product enhancement (title + description + caption in one call) |
| GET | `/generations` | JWT (seller) | List past generations (paginated) |
| GET | `/generations/{id}` | JWT (seller) | Get generation result |
| GET | `/usage` | JWT (seller) | Current month usage vs tier limits |

### 4.3 Studio Service Logic

```
StudioService
  ├── generate_title(image, category, keywords)
  │     → Analyze image → GPT-4o-mini → Return 3 title options
  │
  ├── generate_description(title, image, category, tone)
  │     → Context-aware prompt → GPT-4o-mini → SEO-optimized description
  │
  ├── generate_caption(product_name, platform, tone)
  │     → Platform-specific prompt (IG vs X vs TikTok) → caption + hashtags
  │
  ├── generate_image(text_prompt, style, product_context)
  │     → DALL·E 3 → Image bytes → Upload to S3/R2 → Return URL
  │
  ├── remove_background(image_url)
  │     → Remove.bg API → Processed image → Upload to S3/R2 → Return URL
  │
  └── enhance_product(product_id)
        → Parallel: generate title + description + caption → Return all
```

### 4.4 Usage Limits (Per Subscription)

| Feature | Free | Pro ($9/mo) | Business ($29/mo) |
|---------|------|-------------|-------------------|
| Caption generations | 10/month | Unlimited | Unlimited |
| Description generations | 10/month | Unlimited | Unlimited |
| Title generations | 10/month | Unlimited | Unlimited |
| Image generations | 5/month | 30/month | Unlimited |
| Background removal | 5/month | 50/month | Unlimited |
| Full product enhance | 3/month | 20/month | Unlimited |

### 4.5 Prompt Templates (`studio/prompts.py`)

Centralized, versioned prompt templates with:
- **Prompt injection sanitization**: Strip system prompt overrides from user inputs
- **Platform-specific formatting**: Instagram (max 2200 chars, 30 hashtags), X (280 chars), TikTok (150 chars)
- **Tone options**: Professional, casual, luxury, playful, minimal
- **Category context**: Fashion, beauty, electronics, food — tailored vocabulary

