## 6. API Endpoints (Full)

### 6.1 Auth — `/api/v1/auth`

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/register` | Register (seller or buyer) |
| POST | `/login` | Login → access + refresh tokens |
| POST | `/refresh` | Rotate access token |
| POST | `/logout` | Revoke refresh token |
| POST | `/forgot-password` | Password reset email |
| POST | `/reset-password` | Reset with token |
| POST | `/verify-email` | Email verification |
| POST | `/verify-phone` | Send phone OTP |
| POST | `/verify-phone/confirm` | Confirm OTP |
| POST | `/mfa/setup` | TOTP setup |
| POST | `/mfa/verify` | Activate MFA |
| POST | `/mfa/disable` | Disable MFA (requires TOTP) |
| POST | `/google` | Google OAuth |

### 6.2 Users — `/api/v1/users`

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/me` | Current user profile |
| PATCH | `/me` | Update profile |
| PUT | `/me/password` | Change password |
| DELETE | `/me` | Delete account (GDPR) |
| GET | `/me/data-export` | Export data (GDPR) |
| GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE | `/me/addresses/*` | Saved addresses CRUD |

### 6.3 Sellers — `/api/v1/seller`

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/profile` | Create seller profile |
