| PUT | `/profile/payout` | Connect bank (requires MFA) |
| POST | `/profile/kyc` | Submit KYC documents |
| GET/POST | `/profile/subscription` | Billing & tier management |
| POST/DELETE | `/team/{member_id}` | Team management (Phase 3) |

### 6.4 Products — `/api/v1/products`

